J00-4002:1	204:700	3.3 Ellipsis Not surprisingly, we can adapt a version of the HOU approach to ellipsis resolution (Dalrymple, Shieber, and Pereira 1991; Pulman 1991; Gawron 1992, 1995) very easily within this framework.
